**Constraints:**
- Do NOT modify build configuration or add new dependencies.
- `bun lint` and `bun typecheck` must pass.

---

## Critical Files

| File | Role |
|---|---|
| `packages/shared/src/theme.ts` | **NEW** — theme types + 3 built-in definitions |
| `packages/shared/package.json` | Add `./theme` subpath export |
| `apps/web/src/hooks/useTheme.ts` | **REWRITE** — named-theme external store |
| `apps/web/src/components/ThemeProvider.tsx` | **NEW** — provider component |
| `apps/web/src/components/ThemeSelector.tsx` | **NEW** — selector with swatches |
| `apps/web/src/router.ts` | Mount `ThemeProvider` in `Wrap` |
| `apps/web/src/routes/_chat.settings.tsx` | Replace theme UI with `<ThemeSelector />` |

