Renders a radio-group of theme buttons. Each button contains a `ThemeSwatch` — a 72×48 px mini-preview built entirely with inline styles (no new CSS classes needed).

Swatch layout (illustrative):
```
┌──────────────────────┐
│sidebar│ ──────────── │  ← foreground lines (0.6 / 0.3 opacity)
│ strip │              │
│       │          ●   │  ← accent dot
│       ├──────────────│
│       │  status bar  │
└──────────────────────┘
```

